quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  10,11,"Sinno Alla yaccinanayno yim…ďe …ďen bone wano O yacciniranta …ďe mo∆ī∆īere, lajal ma…ď…ďe ngal timminanteno …ďe. Men acca …ďen …ďe tam∆īinaaki hawrugol e Amen e bewre ma…ď…ďe nden hi…ďe bumam-bumannoo"
  10,12,"Si lorra memii ne…ó…óanke on, o nodda men …ďaŇčŇče makko, maa ko joo…óii…óo, maa ko o darii…óo. Tuma nde Men huncini mo lorra makko kan, o fe∆ī∆īira wa si o noddaano Men e lorra memuka mo. Ko wano non fantinoo…ďe …ďen cu…óiranaa kon ko …ďe gollaynoo"
  10,13,"Gom…óii Men halkiino gire adinoo…ďe on nde …ďe too√Īunoo, Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen addani …ďe …ďanngannduyeeji. ∆Āe wonaano gom…óinoo…ďe. Ko wana nii Men yo…ďirta yim…ďe bom…ďe …ďen"
  10,14,"Refti Men Men wa…ói on lontotoo…ďe ka leydi …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, ha min ndaara no gollirton"
  10,15,"Si Aayeeje Amen …ďanngu…óe …óen janngaama e dow ma…ď…ďe, …ďen …ďe tam∆īinaaki hawrugol e Amen wi'a: \"Addu Alqur'aanaare goo hara wanaa ndee …óoo\" maa \"wostonde\". Maaku : \"Haananaa lam nde mi wa…ótitira nde immorde e …ďaŇčŇče wonkii am. Mi jokkataa si wanaa kon ko wahayinaa e am. Min mi…óo huli si mi yeddii Joomi am, lepte √Īalaande mawnde"
  10,16,"Maaku : \"Sinno Alla muuyuno, mi janngataano nde e dow moo…óon, mi aanndintaande mon kadi. Gom…óii mi √Īii…ďiino e moo…óon nguurndamado may- re. E on haqqiltaa"
  10,17,"Alaa …ďur…óo too√Īude haa hewta on fefindii…óo fenaande e hoore Alla, maa o fenni Aayeeje Makko …óen. Si ko woni, o malnatah bom…ďe …ďen"
  10,18,"Hi…ďe rewa gaanin Alla kon ko lorrataa …ďe nafataa …ďe, hi…ďe wi'a : \"Ko …óii …óoo woni tefanooji men …óin ka Alla\". Maaku : \"E on yeetoto Alla ko O anndaa ka kammuuli wanaa ka leydi?\" Senayee woodanii Mo, O toowii gaay e ko …ďe sirkata"
  10,19,"Yim…ďe …ďen laatanooki si wanaa mofte goote. ∆Āe lurri. Sinno wanaa konngol adinoo ngol immorde ka Joomi maa, √Īaaweteno hakkunde ma…ď…ďe e kon ko …ďe lurraynoo"
  10,20,"Hi…ďe wi'a : \"Ko ha…ónoo Aaya jippinee e makko immorde ka Joomi makko?\" Maaku : \"Annde ko wirnii kon ko Alla woodanii.Habbitee; min komi habbitii…óo wonndude e mo'on"
  10,21,"Si Men mee…óinirii yim…ďe …ďen yurmeende …ďaawo lorra memnooka …ďe, jaka yoo hi…ďe mari pewje e Aayeeje Amen …óen. Maaku : \"Ko Alla …ďuri yaawude fewjoore\". Pellet, Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen hino winnda kon ko fewjoton"
  10,22,"Ko kanko woni doginoowo on ka njorndi e ka maayo, haa si on wonii ka laa…óe, …óe doginira …ďe henndu laa…ďndu, …ďe weltora ndu. Ara e majje henndu bippooru, molloo…óe (bempejje) …óen ara e ma…ď…ďe immorde e kala baŇčŇče, …ďe fellita wonnde kam…ďe …ďe hu…ďindaama, …ďe toroo Alla ko …ďe la…ď…ďinana Mo diina kan, […ďe wi'a]: \"Si A da…óndii men e …óum …óoo, pellet, men laatoday e yettoo…ďe [Ma] …ďen"
  10,23,"∆Āaawo nde O da…óndi …ďe, e jaka yoo kam…ďe hi…ďe bewira ko leydi ko adaa e goonga. Ko onon yo yim…ďe, anndee bewre mon nden yantay e wonkiiji mon. Ko dakamme nguurndam aduna. Refti ko ka Amen woni rutorde mon, Men yeetitoo on ko laatino…óon gollayno…óon"
  10,24,"Anndee misal nguurndam aduna …óam, ko wano ndiyam …óam Men jippini immorde ka kammu, pu…ói leydi ndin jillondira e majjam …óum ko yim…ďe e neemoraa…ói √Īaamata. Haa si ndi leydi ndi ∆īettii cu…óaari mayri ndi cu…óike, yim…ďe mayri …ďen jikka wonnde ko …ďe hattam…ďe (so√Īugol) e mayri, yami- roore Amen ardira e mayri jemma maa √Īalorma, Men wa…óa (pu…ói) …óin so√Īaa…ói wa si tawii …ói mo∆ī- ∆īaano hanki mun. Ko wano nii Men fensitirta Aayeeje …óen wonannde yim…ďe miijitotoo…ďe …ďen"
  10,25,"Alla no nodda on faade e galle kisal, Himo fewna on Mo o muyyi faade e laawol focciingol ngol"